  "description": "Ouroboros' chaotic attractor bleeds directly into Ombre's memory/forgetting blend axis. The strange attractor is a narrator — when chaos peaks, memory collapses into the present; when the attractor pulls inward, forgetting dominates the sonic texture. Perception and amnesia oscillate in the orbit of a Lorenz basin. Neither engine leads. The chaos decides.",
